Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:05.99,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,他应该一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:07.94,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你讲的好像这事情跟你无关似的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:09.74,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,那种人能相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:54.74,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,从古拉多斯来的那个人告诉我们 地球正被觊觎着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:58.48,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我相信他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:06.54,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,当我看到他的眼睛时 我就要相信他 不相信他不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:07.94,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:19.37,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,那个人 又救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:21.38,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,如同我所相信的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:41.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1010)\b0\3c&HE5F3CB&}古拉多斯三足式运输船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:27.31,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)}逃出心中的留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:55.40,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,那小鬼 不可以小看他 下次一定加倍还给他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:02.02,Default_Sub,Pilot,0,0,0,,不好意思 请向总部报告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:03.08,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:07.27,Default_Sub,Pilot,0,0,0,,是 司令说 必须向总部报告作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:08.83,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,不要多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:11.30,Default_Sub,Pilot,0,0,0,,可是必须要汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.03,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,这里的指挥官是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:14.66,Default_Sub,Pilot,0,0,0,,那当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.52,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,指挥官说不用报告了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:24.83,Default_Sub,Pilot B,0,0,0,,机器人的紧急修理已完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:25.89,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,好 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:26.74,Default_Sub,PIlot,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:47.90,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1010)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}雷兹纳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.89,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,在这里一直想也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:26.83,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,要到最近的美军基地才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.08,Default_Sub,Man2,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.42,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,他会一直犹豫也是当然的 我们一点防备也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.42,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,如果又被敌人途中埋伏的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:36.68,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,所以你想 我们还能待在这多久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:40.25,Default_Sub,Man2,0,0,0,,外面是地狱 这里也是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:45.27,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我能说句话吗 去美国基地那边没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:46.51,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:50.68,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,发生了这么大的事 可是战机却只有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.35,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,在敌人刚出现的时候才有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.20,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,可是后来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:57.04,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,现在是在讨论要不要去 不要把话题拉大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.65,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是这样没错 但你没注意到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:03.96,Default_Sub,Woman,0,0,0,,与其随便乱动 说不定在那少年身边还比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:06.79,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,你知道他的真面目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.33,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,看着真是碍眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:29.44,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我留在这里把引敌人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:33.38,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,请趁这个时候快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:38.91,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,真是假惺惺的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:42.48,Default_Sub,ManB,0,0,0,,与其被他保护 还不如被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.53,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.52,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我不想被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:48.42,Default_Sub,MabB,0,0,0,,你怎么这么说 小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:50.24,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,请快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.64,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,他们一定还会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.52,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,快听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.60,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,现在马上离开这里 趁着还有风暴离开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:05.87,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,如果再拖时间的话 风暴会走的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.48,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,有人反对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.34,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.35,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,你还在干什么 快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.07,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,雷 还要多久才能动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:25.79,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,根据模式的不同 时间会有所变化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.69,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,如果是战斗模式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:35.09,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,如果是战斗模式的话 推测的可动时间8.27±20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:38.03,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,武器的使用方面 要用激光的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:53.56,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,总之 要让他们以为里面还有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:06.04,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,辅助动力源应该还能用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.35,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.78,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我们如果被发现的话就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.65,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你还真冷血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:45.37,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,如果他是以别的方式出现在我们面前就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.97,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,可是总觉得哪里怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:52.08,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,他应该一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.81,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你讲的好像这事跟你无关似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.64,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,那种人能相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:09:00.81,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,那是事实 不管大家对他的感觉如何 他说的事都实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.97,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,他会出现是因为敌人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:47.05,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,警报 有三架SPT侵入侦测范围
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.10,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.43,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,那些猴崽子还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:13.87,Default_Sub,PilotA,0,0,0,,赏他们导弹吃吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:15.88,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,笨蛋 怎么能用导弹这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.79,Default_Sub,PilotA,0,0,0,,为什么 这样不是最有破坏力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:22.60,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,吵死了 美食要慢慢的品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:28.23,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1010)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}布尔格伦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:35.23,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1010)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}无畏者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.55,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.67,Default_Sub,Pilot,0,0,0,,他们好像没有要出来的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:23.48,Default_Sub,PilotB,0,0,0,,我们要潜进去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:26.56,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,听好了 没有我的命令不要随便乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.31,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,多米利亚 你去另一边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:59.19,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,嘉斯坦 你从中间突入 连地球人一起杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.06,Default_Sub,Roberia/Kassen,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.91,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,无论如何都要设法争取更多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:29.75,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,备用战斗燃料箱还有98单位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.90,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,离战斗还有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.26,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:21.69,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.43,Default_Sub,Kaseen,0,0,0,,连半个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:25.63,Default_Sub,Kaseen,0,0,0,,地球人会不会跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.27,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:28.79,Default_Sub,Kassen,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:32.91,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,先别管那个 我们还有一个小时的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.92,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,那家伙还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:11.52,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,受到严重撞击 逃生装置无法启动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:14.02,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,嘉斯坦 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:22.90,Default_Sub,Kassen,0,0,0,,我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.27,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:36.69,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,你是我的人质了 你们通讯的频率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:43.71,Default_Sub,Kaseen,0,0,0,,MS132-5200
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:48.08,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,把通话频段定在 MS132 - 5200Mhz
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.97,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,怎么了嘉斯坦 回答我 嘉斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.12,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,他已经是我的人质了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:52.97,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:57.58,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,想要他无事的话 就离开SPT到这来 听到了没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.65,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:05.38,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,好像留在这基地的只有你一个人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:09.37,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不照我说的做的话 你的部下就要没命了 我等你五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:14.54,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,那句话应该是我跟你说的 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:15.59,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:18.25,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,要杀要剐随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.82,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:26.33,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,我也等你五分钟 只要你把雷兹纳交出来 我可以饶你不死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:28.52,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,真的让我杀了他也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.54,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,他是你的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:34.66,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,我才不管 要怎么样随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.96,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,听好了 只有五分钟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.75,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,你给我待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:57.09,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,过了三十秒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:15.34,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,能源补充中  存量增加2单位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:18.79,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,还有三分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:23.49,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,队长 他如果被逼急了 很可能真的会杀了嘉斯坦的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:25.87,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,吵死了 不要顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:26.73,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.06,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,不要再说些有的没的 快去追地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:31.82,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,他们还没走远 发现他们的话马上就杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.03,Default_Sub,Roberia,0,0,0,,是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.33,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.85,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不准让他去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:46.87,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:48.30,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,部下出事也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.13,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,还有两分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:00.24,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,风越来越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:03.20,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,这种风力刚好可以隐藏我们车子的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.89,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,不过再大下去就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.80,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,到这里才走了一半是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:08.96,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:12.41,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,拜托 希望可以平安到达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:16.52,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,那家伙现在还在战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:19.79,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,敌人没追来的话就应该没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.61,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:23.92,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我觉得他应该是在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:28.80,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,至少我是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:34.26,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,如果我们能平安到达的话 应该好好感谢他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:40.30,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,他现在为了救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:45.65,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,还有三十秒 小鬼 快放弃 给我乖乖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:48.59,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,快来把你的部下带回去 我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:51.84,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,小鬼 你还想逃到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.28,Default_Sub,Kassen,0,0,0,,队长请救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:57.11,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,能源存量只剩一单位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.99,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,资讯信息系统无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:01.42,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,还剩15秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.78,Default_Sub,Kassen,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:03.91,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不要吵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:04.98,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,11秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:05.82,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:06.79,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:07.86,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:08.82,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:09.77,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:10.72,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.74,Default_Sub_Top,Rey,0,0,0,,能源存量用尽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:11.78,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:12.74,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:13.89,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.29,Default_Sub_Top,Gosterro,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.30,Default_Sub,Kassen,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.95,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.50,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:48.24,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,能源存量剩余0单位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:50.29,Default_Sub,Kassen,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:54.31,Default_Sub,Kassen,0,0,0,,为什么不开枪 地球人的话应该做得到的 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:57.39,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我身体里的血有一半是古拉多斯人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.56,Default_Sub,Kaseen,0,0,0,,一半
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:04.39,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我的妈妈跟你一样也是古拉多斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:23.66,Default_Sub,Kassen,0,0,0,,可恶 连我都要杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.26,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,准备出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:25.95,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:42.34,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,明明就不会杀人 小鬼 给我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:50.10,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,你这小鬼 让你看看我的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:59.59,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,战斗信息 目标转变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:01.31,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.95,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,战斗就要像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:15.60,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,遭到攻击 轻微受损
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:18.27,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,瞄准敌人SPT中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:22.59,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,重复 瞄准敌人SPT中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:29.78,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:45.40,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,这下你终于束手无策 到地面上来跟我打了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:49.90,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,小鬼 你就听着自己的心跳死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.45,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.68,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,更换能源 能源透支
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:08.38,Default_Sub,Kassen,0,0,0,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:10.50,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,你这家伙 竟把枪对准我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:13.18,Default_Sub,Kassen,0,0,0,,你能说的只有这句话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:18.36,Default_Sub,Kassen,0,0,0,,小子 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.81,Default_Sub,Kassen,0,0,0,,你还在等什么 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:30.51,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:34.72,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,更换能源 能源透支 激光枪无法充能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:12.70,Default_Sub,Gosterro,0,0,0,,混蛋 竟敢跟我作对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:43.32,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,那少年被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:50.21,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,当新的敌人出现在我们面前时 大家是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.16,0:23:56.08,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们才不要你来保护我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:23:59.08,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在你们的星球都不会打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.71,0:24:02.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,他想把我们都杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:08.43,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\c&HF9E5EA&\pos(710,770)}即使被保护，但又...{\c&HF9E5EA&}
